Footer implementation spec
Goals

Consistent across site

Strong internal linking (SEO)

Clear trust signals (disclaimer + sources)

Newsletter conversion (Join Free)

Clean, premium look

Layout (desktop)

4-column grid

Brand + short positioning + social

Explore (core sections)

Tools (key tools)

Legal + Contact + Newsletter CTA

Content rules

Use real HTML links

Include a short disclaimer

Include “Source” line on market-data pages via component prop later, but footer can include general language

Add location hint: Montreal

SEO rules

Include links to your main hubs and key subpages

Anchor text should match page intent (no “click here”)

Keep footer links consistent sitewide (helps crawl)

Reference implementation


